{"tid":2114651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Instagram數週內推出Reels，跟抖音一樣主打15秒影片","createTime":"2020-07-19T04:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T11:25:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":67,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"df8fff234097c9acbad00db5c3b98f769584a109","tid":2114651,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/107704374_752737465537908_741547522098831144_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=j6G2m_K1mPoAX82Zx9G&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=744f36842d179b109101b6c282c4c6d8&amp;oe=5F39B35D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F107704374_752737465537908_741547522098831144_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3Dj6G2m_K1mPoAX82Zx9G%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D744f36842d179b109101b6c282c4c6d8%26oe%3D5F39B35D&h=bb112bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《NBC》引述消息，Instagram 會在8月初在美國和全球超過 50 個國家推出最新短片上載服務 Instagram Reels，更會以開放至全球用戶作目標。時機正好在印度剛封殺海外版抖音TikTok，而美國亦在考慮封殺TikTok之際。<br />\n<br />\nInstagram Reels 的性質與 TikTok 相若，用家可發佈 15 秒短片或一系列音樂作品。用家更可到「Featured Reels」欄目留意成為網絡潮流的影片。<br />\n<br />\nInstagram Reels 早於去年 11 月已在巴西試驗推出、上個月擴大服務範圍至德國和法國，上星期引入印度，剛好是印度宣佈禁用 TikTok 之後的一日。至於下一輪推出的地區會包括美國、英國、日本、墨西哥和另外 50 個國家地區。香港在什麼時候能用Instagram Reels？尚待進一步消息公佈。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Tiktok 在美國有超過5,000萬日活躍用戶，深受年輕人歡迎。今次Instagram Reels的推出能否搶佔TikTok的市場？<br />\n<br />\n消息來源：NBC"},{"pid":"7d6bd54744e985caf31976703fc67f8661c4bcc6","tid":2114651,"uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc96756814bb3ec08b746b081a0824e8dfd16a66","tid":2114651,"uid":39215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那野可以收皮了"},{"pid":"66237a2678bf6f648a0e5002d1627c8c62290f37","tid":2114651,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"朱仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e2deabc293adc133142dd4a75ff7ae9f010130","tid":2114651,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/article/business/4507/ig/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2F4507%2Fig%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=0edeb7a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/article/business/4507/ig/</a>"},{"pid":"b140a72b508f9d30fd90924cff3c1ba67258c957","tid":2114651,"uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"雖然facebook公司都係垃圾<br />\n但支持ig打敗抖陰"},{"pid":"7a5704f4073331bf974e3b6c81038b000d60560b","tid":2114651,"uid":21602,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:08:56.000Z","msg":"朱西：If you can&rsquo;t join them, beat them."},{"pid":"9edaac1e75d3b0e218e023d9c8d224d943e7a883","tid":2114651,"uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"facebook同騰訊手法越嚟越似，一係就收購對手，一係就自己整同類app，用user base打殘對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知點解15秒影片會紅，不過打殘tiktok係好事嚟"},{"pid":"116f096da71d75c53a4841ca3e9b22846b409327","tid":2114651,"uid":16775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9edaac1e75d3b0e218e023d9c8d224d943e7a883","tid":2114651,"uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"facebook同騰訊手法越嚟越似，一係就收購對手，一係就自己整同類app，用user base打殘對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知點解15秒影片會紅，不過打殘tiktok係好事嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:11: